==English==
===Noun===
'''pipe wrench'''

# An adjustable [[wrench]] (British [[spanner]]) with a toothed jaw for gripping [[pipe]], frequently used by a [[plumber]] or [[pipe fitter]], to loosen and tighten pipes with threaded connections.

